\item [4)] shudAdhxMtaHkaraNanU satayxsaMdhanU niVti shAsatxrXda naDeyananxritavanU dhiVmaMtanU Adavanu mAtarx oLeLxya sahAya paDedu daMDavanunx nayana mADabahudu. uLidavarige daMDaniVtiyu dakakx\-lAradu. 
